Yeah, I think this feature is useful, at now, I have got to write a loop by myself to mine some blocks as following:
```js
async function mineBlocks(blockNumber) {
  while (blockNumber > 0) {
    blockNumber--;
    await hre.network.provider.request({
      method: "evm_mine",
      params: [],
    });
  }
}
```
So it will be great if I can pass a parameter for `evm_mine`.

